&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for a post at a DGH with a big heart, in a beautiful location in Hampshire and where you can be part of an innovative Consultant led service? Then join us and help support and develop the quality of our front line team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Acute Physicians who share our values as well as our vision to provide a robust, sustainable and integrated 7 day ambulatory service including nurse led clinics, supported speciality interests, and reduced length of stay and most importantly a patient centered service.&lt;/p&gt;
